<?php $__env->startSection('content'); ?><p>Keke Palmer posed in a hot pink bikini Sunday on social media while sharing a tidbit of her new song Dreamcatcher.</p>

<p>The 27-year-old entertainer sparkled in the short video clip that she shared with her roughly 9.9 million followers on Instagram.</p>

<p>Keke in the video stood in shallow pool water in her bright bikini and beamed while putting her hand on top of her long, curly hair as she struck a pose.</p>

<p>Dreamy song: Keke Palmer posed in a hot pink bikini Sunday on social media while sharing a tidbit of her new song Dreamcatcher</p>

<p>The opening lines to her new song Dreamcatcher were then heard, 'Hope it helps you sleep' and Keke also wrote 'Dreamcatcher' in the caption.</p>

<p>Keke glittered with the help of a filter and smiled as she apparently missed her mark singing along to the tune.</p>

<p>The Illinois native released her third EP titled Virgo Tendencies, Pt. 1 in August through her record label Big Bosses Entertainment.</p>

<p>Dreamcatcher was the second song on the 12-track project.</p>

<p>Sparkling star: The 27-year-old entertainer sparkled in the short video clip that she shared with her roughly 9.9 million followers on Instagram</p>

<p>Cute smile: Keke in the video stood in shallow pool water in her bright bikini and beamed while putting her hand on top of her long, curly hair as she struck a pose</p>

<p>Glittering gal: Keke glittered with the help of a filter and smiled as she apparently missed her mark lip syncing to the tune</p>

<p>Keke last week hosted the 2020 MTV Video Music Awards from New York City amid the coronavirus pandemic.</p>

<p>She performed her song Snack that was released in July as the third single from her EP.</p>

<p>Disney+ announced last month that Keke will voice a new character in the upcoming revival The Proud Family: Louder and Prouder.</p>

<p>Awards show: The Illinois native last week hosted the 2020 MTV Video Music Awards from New York City amid the coronavirus pandemic</p>

<p>Keke will voice 14-year-old activist Maya Leibowitz-Jenkins in the upcoming animated series.</p>

<p>The streaming service also shared some artwork of Maya, depicting a fierce teenage girl wearing grey jeans, sneakers and an ochre colored zip up.</p>

<p>Maya has her brunette hair cornrows with some bright red highlights and in the image was standing proud with her cartoon fist raised and a look of determination on her face.</p>

<p>The original Proud Family cartoon aired on the Disney Channel from 2001-2005, and no release date has been announced yet for its reboot.</p>

<p>Voice role: Keke will voice 14-year-old activist Maya Leibowitz-Jenkins in the upcoming animated reboot The Proud Family: Louder and Prouder on Disney+</p>
